It removes the skin, see?

1573
01:46:28,714 --> 01:46:30,448
An object from our Brothers
at the smithy's invention.

1574
01:46:35,621 --> 01:46:37,590
May I see Mother later, please?

1575
01:46:38,256 --> 01:46:39,658
Mother Ann will be here
for supper.

1576
01:46:39,758 --> 01:46:41,293
She meant our mother.

1577
01:46:41,794 --> 01:46:44,497
Sister Martha
will also be at supper.

1578
01:46:51,270 --> 01:46:54,340
<i>♪ I love Mother ♪</i>

1579
01:46:54,440 --> 01:46:57,743
<i>♪ I love her way ♪</i>

1580
