1670
01:54:45,853 --> 01:54:47,154
Good evening!

1671
01:54:47,588 --> 01:54:49,223
Make room! Make room!

1672
01:54:49,991 --> 01:54:51,058
Move closer!

1673
01:54:53,360 --> 01:54:56,798
Seeing that so many have
come to join us this night,

1674
01:54:56,898 --> 01:54:59,266
please exercise patience

1675
01:54:59,366 --> 01:55:02,103
in passing through to sit in
the presence of our Mother Ann.

1676
01:55:03,405 --> 01:55:04,839
Forbearance, I say!

1677
01:55:07,342 --> 01:55:10,378
We have founded
six new settlements

1678
01:55:10,478 --> 01:55:13,215
in New Lebanon, in New York,

1679
01:55:14,549 --> 01:55:17,119
Enfield in Connecticut,

1680
01:55:17,219 --> 01:55:19,987
and Hancock, Harvard, Shirley,

1681
01:55:20,422 --> 01:55:22,624
and Tyringham in Massachusetts.

1682
01:55:22,724 --> 01:55:25,693
And now, at Petersham.

1683
01:55:25,793 --> 01:55:26,995
Pardon me.

1684
01:55:27,095 --> 01:55:28,863
WILLIAM: There shall be
a place for each of you!

1685
01:55:32,067 --> 01:55:32,968
WOMAN: Pardon me.

1686
01:55:34,736 --> 01:55:35,737
Excuse me.

1687
01:55:37,072 --> 01:55:38,573
Excuse me.
Let the children through.

1688
01:55:40,475 --> 01:55:41,409
Coming through.

1689
01:55:41,509 --> 01:55:42,577
GIRL: Mother?

1690
01:55:42,678 --> 01:55:43,946
WOMAN: Mother.

1691
01:55:44,046 --> 01:55:46,615
- GIRL: Is that her?
- WOMAN: Is it really you?

1692
01:55:46,715 --> 01:55:48,283
ANN: Yes, Child.

1693
01:55:48,383 --> 01:55:50,485
Do not be frightened, lassies.

1694
01:55:50,586 --> 01:55:52,721
(OVERLAPPING CHATTER)

1695
01:55:52,821 --> 01:55:55,991
Oh, dear. It delights me so
to make your acquaintance.

1696
01:55:57,493 --> 01:56:00,629
Come nearer to me.
I am your Mother.

1697
01:56:00,729 --> 01:56:01,764
Do not be shy.

1698
01:56:03,432 --> 01:56:05,768
They must find
themselves befuddled.

1699
01:56:05,868 --> 01:56:06,969
Let me explain.

1700
01:56:07,135 --> 01:56:09,004
I am your Mother,
and your mother's Mother.

1701
01:56:09,104 --> 01:56:12,275
We shall erect edifice
here at Petersham.

1702
01:56:12,841 --> 01:56:14,443
I call on you,
Brothers and Sisters,

1703
01:56:14,543 --> 01:56:16,845
to aid in this endeavor.

1704
01:56:16,945 --> 01:56:18,914
MAN: You shall never build here!

1705
01:56:19,014 --> 01:56:20,349
Knock out the lights!

1706
01:56:20,449 --> 01:56:22,986
(CRASHING, SCREAMING)

1707
01:56:23,086 --> 01:56:24,753
MARY: Surround Mother.
Protect her!

1708
01:56:24,853 --> 01:56:26,422
ANN: Stay calm, Children!

1709
01:56:26,522 --> 01:56:27,323
MAN: Coming through.

1710
01:56:27,423 --> 01:56:28,925
ANN: God is with us!

1711
01:56:29,025 --> 01:56:30,927
WILLIAM:
Do not fight back, Brothers!

1712
01:56:31,027 --> 01:56:32,428
MAN: Where is she?

1713
01:56:32,528 --> 01:56:33,830
WILLIAM: Protect Mother Ann!

1714
01:56:33,930 --> 01:56:35,131
MAN: Show us the witch!

1715
01:56:35,231 --> 01:56:36,900
ANN: Do not fight back!

1716
01:56:37,400 --> 01:56:38,367
MAN: Take the Brother!

1717
01:56:41,570 --> 01:56:42,305
ANN: Brother!

1718
01:56:46,576 --> 01:56:48,578
MAN: This land is not yours.

1719
01:56:48,678 --> 01:56:51,247
You shall never live here.
You shall never build here.

1720
01:56:51,347 --> 01:56:53,783
ANN: Mrs. Shattuck,
let me go to Brother William!

1721
01:56:53,883 --> 01:56:55,685
Let me go!

1722
01:56:55,785 --> 01:56:58,988
