1728
01:57:07,531 --> 01:57:09,233
WILLIAM: Do not fight back,
Brothers!

1729
01:57:10,066 --> 01:57:11,101
ANN: Mary!

1730
01:57:11,535 --> 01:57:13,803
MARY: Mother!
(GRUNTING)

1731
01:57:13,903 --> 01:57:14,871
