- No!

1733
01:57:18,142 --> 01:57:20,810
WILLIAM: Take your filthy hands
off my sister!

1734
01:57:20,910 --> 01:57:22,079
ANN: William!

1735
01:57:22,179 --> 01:57:24,814
WOMAN: Mary! Mary!

1736
01:57:25,515 --> 01:57:26,350
