1739
01:57:34,725 --> 01:57:36,560
WOMAN: Oh, please have mercy.

1740
01:57:36,661 --> 01:57:40,164
No! No! No!

1741
01:57:40,264 --> 01:57:42,432
ANN: God, please!

1742
01:57:43,534 --> 01:57:44,635
Please.

1743
01:57:44,735 --> 01:57:46,471
(ANN SCREAMS)

1744
01:57:49,907 --> 01:57:53,243
MAN: She is not a she at all!
Her sex must be examined.

1745
01:57:53,678 --> 01:57:55,045
Tear off her skirts!

1746
01:57:55,145 --> 01:57:57,014
(ANN GRUNTING)

1747
01:57:58,182 --> 01:58:00,518
