1748
01:58:02,520 --> 01:58:04,255
A eunuch, I reckon.

1749
01:58:04,355 --> 01:58:05,723
There's no phallus.

1750
01:58:05,823 --> 01:58:07,325
Did you cut it off, witch?

1751
01:58:07,425 --> 01:58:10,928
I forgive you for your sins,
and I will pray for your souls.

1752
01:58:11,029 --> 01:58:12,563
Pray for them, Mary!

1753
01:58:13,131 --> 01:58:16,667
Father, forgive them,
for they know not what they do!

1754
01:58:17,268 --> 01:58:19,971
She has all the right parts,
but she is not a woman.

1755
01:58:21,172 --> 01:58:24,509
Rank, she is. It is.
Whatever you are.

1756
01:58:24,609 --> 01:58:25,977
(GUNFIRE IN DISTANCE)

1757
01:58:26,077 --> 01:58:26,912
What is that?

1758
01:58:27,012 --> 01:58:28,446
