1765
01:58:48,567 --> 01:58:50,869
Brother! Wake up.

1766
01:58:51,236 --> 01:58:52,771
Brother James!

1767
01:58:55,006 --> 01:58:56,642
No!

1768
01:59:00,612 --> 01:59:03,014
