<i>♪ And rolling river of Jordan ♪</i>

1780
02:00:28,268 --> 02:00:30,871
<i>♪ I will go ♪</i>

1781
02:00:33,140 --> 02:00:38,912
<i>♪ I will be baptized again ♪</i>

1782
02:00:39,947 --> 02:00:44,818
<i>♪ I will not stand alone ♪</i>

